=== 2026-02-21 19:30 — Real UPCitemdb API client ===
- Added UpcItemDbLookupService to UpcLookupService.kt — real API client for UPCitemdb
  - Free tier: GET https://api.upcitemdb.com/prod/trial/lookup?upc=... (no API key needed)
  - Uses java.net.http.HttpClient (standard library) + Jackson ObjectMapper (transitive via Vaadin)
  - HTTP 200 → parse items[0], extract title/brand/description/category
  - HTTP 404 → found=false (valid response, counts against quota)
  - HTTP 429 → apiError=true (rate limited, don't count against quota, retry later)
  - Other errors → apiError=true
  - detectMediaFormat() scans title/category/description for keywords:
    "4k uhd"/"ultra hd"/"uhd" → UHD_BLURAY, "hd dvd" → HD_DVD,
    "blu-ray"/"bluray" → BLURAY, "dvd" → DVD
  - No new dependencies — HttpClient is JDK standard, Jackson is already on classpath
- Changed UpcLookupAgent default from MockUpcLookupService to UpcItemDbLookupService
  - MockUpcLookupService still available via constructor injection for testing
- BUILD SUCCESSFUL
- Files modified: service/UpcLookupService.kt, service/UpcLookupAgent.kt
