- AVURLAssetHTTPHeaderFieldsKey is undocumented/private and only sends
  headers on the initial request — not viable for HLS
- AVAssetResourceLoaderDelegate is NOT called for HLS segment requests
- AVPlayer requires minimum ~10 segments (5 seconds at 0.5s/segment)
  to start playback — 6 segments was insufficient
- Access log ring buffer (200 entries) overflows with 2/sec HLS polls,
  hiding segment requests — they ARE happening, just pushed out

