=== 2026-04-12 21:05 — ForMobile preset fix + re-transcode prioritization ===
- Ffprobe'd an Airwolf episode: ForMobile (1.77 GB) was 2x the ForBrowser
  (0.90 GB) size and bigger than the source MKV. Root cause was two bugs
  cooperating in EncoderProfile.mobileVariant() + TranscodeCommand.buildMobile:
  - Mobile preset used fixed ABR at 5 Mbps (1080p target) regardless of
    source resolution
  - 1080p cap filter was a no-op for SD content so 720x480 DVDs got
    flooded with HD-target bitrate
- Rewrote mobileVariant to mirror the browser CQ/CRF 23 with a 5M
  maxrate cap. Dropped the output cap to 720p (small screens don't
  benefit from 1080p).
- Added mobile_encoder_version stamping: new column on transcode,
  migration V072 sets existing rows to v1, const bumped to v2 in
  EncoderProfile. Eligibility check picks up version-mismatched rows
  as re-transcode candidates. Buddy reports the version it used in
  ReportComplete (added proto field); server stamps on receipt.
- Discovered priority bug: Xena re-transcodes were starving Airwolf
  first-pass (27 first-pass items dominated by 2542 re-transcodes
  because Xena had a wish-vote-driven transcode_priority bump). The
  sort tiered priorityCounts above isReTranscode, so any prioritized
  title's re-transcodes jumped every other title's first-pass work.
  Fix: swap tiers — isReTranscode is now the outermost key, priority
  bumps only order within tiers.
- Fixed separate bug: buddy's File.renameTo(.mp4) silently failed when
  a previous bloated output existed (Windows doesn't overwrite). Added
  replaceAtomically() helper using Files.move(REPLACE_EXISTING).
- Fixed cache-tier bug: the cached-transcode preference previously
  walked the full sorted list, letting cached re-transcodes jump
  ahead of uncached first-pass. Now only applies within the top tier.
- Extracted sort + pick helpers to internal funcs (sortWorkItems,
  pickWinnerId) so unit tests can exercise priority rules directly.
  14 new tests covering first-pass-vs-retranscode, cache preference,
  priority bumps, and for_mobile_requested tier.
- Verified fix: MOBILE PICK log shows top5 is all Airwolf first-pass
  after the redeploy.
- Files: EncoderProfile.kt, TranscodeCommand.kt, proto/buddy.proto,
